### Welcome to Linda's resume page on GitHub.
This is Che, Linda with about one year's and a half work experience as a software engineer. At present, I am studing docker and learning Golang.
A easygoing person.

### What did I do?
Well, I developed Android App by Java on Ubuntu when I was an Intern from 2014, Feb to 2014, Jun.
Then, I came to my current company which is a network security American enterprise, begining developing and maintaining antivirus product library, from 2014, Jun till now. 

### About Education
I graduated from Yanshan University in Jun, 2014 with a Master's degree.

### Key words
C++, Python, Java, Linux, gcc, vi, gdb, OOP, UML.
